reviewText: I grew up surfing with Wayne. This brought back so many memories of Lorne days
Great life story of a extra ordinary surfer and background on how he got there and how he lived his life.

Excellent video portraying the life of Wayne Lynch. The surfing footage is great, the interviews were insightful; really a well made movie. If you surf and don't know who Wayne Lynch is, get this DVD now. If you do know who Wayne Lynch is, you will love this video. Enjoy.
